N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 256.2 - Notice to commissioner

State Regulations

It shall be the duty of food salvagers to notify the
commissioner whenever damaged goods subject to the provisions of article 17-B
are obtained. Notes
